	(text "Running two AO3400A in parallel off a single input.\n3.3V Drive, 1kohm, 3.3mA peak. 3.4us on time (680pF gate capacitance, 5t)\n6.6mA peak total current per pin, MAX from pico is 12mA, configure these pins to 8mA min."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 193.294 158.496 0)
